arStrings.szText: I don't think, I know! (cough) She was born under the blood moon! Everyone knows what that means. (cough)
Self-assured and matter of factly. As if you're talking to an imbicile who doesn't understand simple things.
(cough) I turned sickly right after she was born. She's to blame, and (cough) it's getting worse!
